@alanmcruickshank perfect if you want to clean this up. I think we should do as much as possible under `superset/translations` and get rid of `babel/`.

Also we should probably remove all of the generated files out of the repo, that includes the `.mo` files, `message.json` and maybe more files.

Another nice thing would be to wrap translation processing inside a superset CLI command and simplify CONTRIBUTING.md
